          <p permid="nYE">
          You cannot apply Eisenstein's criterion to the polynomial <m>p(x) = x^3 - 3x + 1</m>.  However, we can apply it to <m>p(x+c)</m> for a carefully picked value of <m>c</m>.
            <ol permid="OxF">
              <li permid="UWL">
